havent updated all that recently... o well, im sure no one minds... i mean do ppl even read this, doubt it, who would care to?... anyhoo, for the sake of myself, ill just pretend that someone reads this & actually cares.. so, yea... umm... not too much to say i guess... lets see..
thursday- stayed afterskoo, hung wit amy... we went to watch ray bowl, it was cool.. i understand how it works now(playing in a league, not just bowling, im not that stupid)... & when they was done(we won), we went to the room with the pool table & were in there for a lil.. it was me, amy, ray, pat, & (sadly) dave... he hit amy, so she was pissed at him, i was annoyed, but him hitting someone isnt news to me.. but other than that, it was alrite.. then when they left, me & amy went to friendlys... we ate, then walked bac to the skool for youth group.. it was kinda stupid, cause it had to do with sex.. o well
friday- went home after skool, but then went to amys & chilled... we watched some of resident evil until we left to go to the movies(to see meet the fockers).. it ended up being just us basically, some other ppl were there we knew, but cause of the lack of seats we didnt sit with them & they left rite after pretty much.. still it was pretty fun.. 'cept the ppl next to us.. eh, the one kid kept hitting on amy & then his friend did for him.. then he started tlking to me.. & the one kid kept hooking up with his gf, it was so annoying & i felt bad for amy... afterwards we waited around til we got picked up
saturday- went to the movies to see white noise with amy, max, jess, ray, monica, elissa, lisa, nicole, alyssa, pat, christine.. it was fun, but the movie itself was bad, it wasnt scary, & the actual plot & junk didnt fully make sense, they like left out alot of info.. anyways, after we walked to willowbrook & ate & chilled.. then it was closing so we left.. went to the ice hockey game, it was cool.. at one point me amy & alyssa went in the arcade.. amy & me played DDR, i suck at it tho.. DP won!! (4-1), but it was great cause we played against Wayne Valley & my cuz is on the team.. my aunt had to drive me home too.. it was great, i was so mean, i made fun of them, arent i such a good person? lol..
sunday- ccd meeting, 2 1/2 hours, about sex... basically- sex is bad, dont have sex, if u have sex u'll die... thats what they were teaching, good stuff.. so stupid.. anyways
monday- sucked, alot... it was horrible... i felt like crap all day.. i just wanted to cry or die cause then things stop... it was so bad.. i felt all alone, & no one would let me tlk, i couldnt tlk to anyone... but, i suppose i should be used to that.. no one really ever listens anyways, even when they do listen.. in the back of everyones minds is always their own problems, they never really focus much on anything else.. no matter how petty their problem(s) is(are), it consumes them & they never really conider that thing may very well be worse for u, so yea.. it sucked... 
tuesday(today)- ehh, it was alrite... not as bad as yesterday.. so of course i pretended to be betterer.. like always.. ur really never allowed to be (openly) upset for more than a day or two.. otherwise, ppl get really annoyed at u, & then things get worse, so yea.. & dont say that thats not true, cause i kno first hand that it is.. anyways... found out some REALLY good news today.. but what sux is that i really wanted to stay after skool today for awhile but they made us all go home cause everything was cancelled.. but do they let us out early? noooo, of course not... errrr... anyhoo.. yea... but i guess it was too bad... well, ill go mr notreallythere... tty sometime again... toodles xox ~Jen       <3 if only u could see that we are meant to be <3  lol

hehe...................... something was kinda funny, the way someone acted towards me today, i doubt that any of u kno who, but o well.... hehe, its interesting.. sry, im done lol... o & anyways.. today was alrite... we got out earlier than early (yes, that makes sense).. we got out after 6th period.. originally we were supposed to get out at 1:45 (periods 'cept 5 & 6 were shortened) but then we got out earlier than that!!.. anyhoo... with the exception of like one or two ppl that i was pissed at, pplz were good today.. o & u kno whats cool?.. i used to live on the same street as ray, a couple of houses down when we were lil, how cool is that? lol... well, fine, i dont care if u dont think its cool, its cool to me, it means we like grew up together kinda & if i never moved, we prolly wouldve hung out & stuff... hmm.. thats really all i got to say i think... well if i wanna say more ill update later... toodles loves! hehe.. xox ~Jen(Jen)

first entry of '05.. cool stuff... well, HAPPY NEW YEAR!!.. yesterday it was like new jenna day lol... i dyed my hair.. i got my new glasses which are kinda cool... AND......... I GOT MY BELLY BUTTON PIERCED!!!.... finally, ive only been waiting since forever lol... its cool tho, i love it, the stone thingy is black, of course lol.. yea, so.. then i went to lizs cause she was having ppl over... it was cool.. cept the slight pain every so often if i hit it or bent the wrong way... o well, it wasnt that bad... but when i went to clean it that nite, i got really dizzy & stuff... because, i had to move the bar up & down, but also when i tried to dry it, i hit it & it moved too much, which is bad, as i have learned lol... anyhoo... today, or er yesterday i suppose... i helped mi madre get food & stuff ready for the (few) ppl coming over... we really didnt do much this year, & i understand why, so whatever.... liz came over & chilled, rang in the new year with me... we made our new years resolutions together, came up with like five, we figure if we get 3 outta 5, we'll be set lol... my main one--- to wake up and not always hate what i see in the mirror.... anyways.. its was alot of fun.. we tlked lots, had good time, at least i hope she had a good time... & im glad, i was hesitant to tell her something, but i REALLY wanted to tlk to her about it.. & her reaction to it was good, she got it the way i did, so i was happy bout that... it was a cool new years 'specially considering i was prepared to be all alone for the new year... so, yea... i just have to say- I HEART LIZ!!!!!!!!!!!!! very bery much!!!.... i think i gonna go now.... toodles my loves... xox ~Jen

hey all... i havent updated in awhile.... anyhoo lots to say & nothing at all really... lets see... tuesday before christmas me & nicole went christmas shopping for pplz, we got the awesomest gifts in the world!.. & we got those kool-aid drinks that u always had when u were little, if u dunno what im tlking about, then ur a loser lol... we spent lots of money hehe, & then she came over & we wrapped them all... wednesday i exchanged gifts with mi chichas at lunch.. gots cool stuff, loved it all, but cant wait to be able to use lizs teehee... thursday we had a mass, it wasnt cool that music ministry had to sit in the bleachers until communion tho...  & we didnt do anything in history afterwards, fun stuff... we just chilled, sat on the desks, ate candy, good times.. nick at one point started dancing with me, just a tad odd lol.. andrew kept playing with his interesting monkey that like vibrated.. a bunch of ppl randomly walked into class... nicole & nicole came, & told us they were buring things in the chem lab, i was tempted to follow them bac when they left  O:-)   hehe... then school ended... we (me, nicole, liz, kaitlin, ana, eric, dana, anetta, cristelle..... & dave) went to charlie browns, but apparently anetta never called in ahead of time so since lots of dp ppl went, we waited like an hour before we got to sit.. but i went to other pplz tables, & ate some of their food & tlked to them of course... it was good times.. i had lots of fun... then on christmas eve, went to mass, then my aunt donnas... didnt do to much... i ate some food, but not that much, wasnt too hungry i guess.... then i basically watched movies by myself (nightmare before christmas & vanhelsing)... my dad really pissed me off cause he started tlkin about stuff he knows nothing about, i hate when he says anything on the matter, cause he knew nothing... i mean, i tried, so hard for.... nvrmd, its just he knows nothing, so he should just, not... whatever....... anyhoo, rather boring, was alone mostly..... christmas, opened stuff, gave stuff..... got a digital camera(ended up gettting a different one today), clothes, dvds, jewlery, hair spray/dye stuff, nuttin too special... then went to my grandmas(not the one thats dead obiously)... didnt do much, ate very little.... watched buffy dvds, by myself of course, tlked a lil to my cuz brennan & christopher, then we went home, & i went in my room.... sunday, didnt do much.... monday, didnt do much..... tuesday, my mom went down the shore with my brother (& hes staying down til tomorrow)... went to the bball game with amy & nicole, met up with jess, mike & ray.... after the game we went to starbucks then charlie browns... then jess & ray left... then we went to starbucks, then mike left... then nicole & amy wanted ice cream so we went to maggie moos.. then they came over & we played DDR, & hung out, at like 8, we drove amy home... nicole stayed til like 10... it was alot of fun, interesting conversations tho, but fun nonetheless, good times.... "not by choice" lol    O:-)    .....hehe, anyhoo.... today i exchanged my digital camera in for a way cooler one :-D    ......then i went to ashleys, it was so weird, & it was kinda sad that zach introduced himself to me, he so cute tho, i miss that i didnt get to be there more..... me & ashley chilled, we played cards, watched a movie & just tlked about stuff, its been so long tho... its kinda sad.... i missed her... & well, now im home, typing this, & hoping i get to do something fun for new years eve..... k, gonna go now..... xox ~Jen~              

 

 *~R.I.P. Grandma~*
